  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb2z7B6iaozxPqCibwUruGKemEUrRnibX9JNRSWAdKbGvDZUylzAkyQkI3jQ311iaKibJDXQQx2NBiaF0Pjw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505171674\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9b11c953&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2z7B6iaozxPqCibwUruGKemEUrRnibX9JNRSWAdKbGvDZUylzAkyQkI3jQ311iaKibJDXQQx2NBiaF0Pjw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：Aeneas</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">首个AI视频生成全球挑战赛来袭，袁粒、颜水成、</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">程明明、</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">田永鸿、Philip Torr多位大佬发起，20万大奖虚位以待！创作大神还是技术极客？两大赛道总有一个适合你，速速点击报名吧。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着AI视频生成技术的飞速发展，「一致性」已成为制约其迈向更高质量、更广应用的核心挑战。视频中时常出现的逻辑谬误、时空错乱、角色风格突变等问题，严重影响了内容的连贯性与可信度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为推动解决这一关键瓶颈，人工智能会议 AAAI 2026 研讨会期间将举办一场专注于此的竞赛——「从片段到原生：视频生成模型中的一致性（CVM）」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"562\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"901\" data-imgfileid=\"505171643\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"901\" data-width=\"901\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bc7ff153&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2z7B6iaozxPqCibwUruGKemEToXxz2JlObHFw2GJ0RFricjxK4ic30DnCdRlgUVj0BJsor5pQwkCgxDg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">由北京大学袁粒</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Li Yuan</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">、田永鸿，联合牛津大学</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Philip Torr</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">、新加坡国立大学颜水成、南开大学程明明、侯淇彬、港科大</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Long Chen</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">、</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Wenhan Luo</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">等共同举办的视频生成一致性挑战赛现已正式开启，一等奖奖金20万。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">旨在建立一个权威的、标准化的评测平台，汇聚全球顶尖的学术与产业力量，共同探索并定义下一代视频生成技术的行业基准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大赛设立两大特色赛道，无论你是技术大神还是创意玩家，都有你的舞台：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">主赛道 (Consistency Track)：硬核技术派的竞技场</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">核心任务：提</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">交你的模型，挑战三大一致性标准，看谁的AI视频最「靠谱」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">世界知识一致性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：视频内的物理规律和常识逻辑是否正确？（比如，水往低处流，人不会突然消失，模型能否理解爱因斯坦最喜欢的乐器是什么？）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">镜头一致性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：平移、缩放、旋转等镜头运动下，画面内容是否平滑过渡，没有断裂感？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">元素ID一致性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：在连续的镜头中，主角的身份ID、外观和场景风格是否保持统一？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">关于这三个一致性的具体解释，参见下面这个视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">评审方式：初赛提交生成视频，决赛需提交模型权重和代码进行复现验证。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">重磅奖励：冠军独揽 20万 人民币现金大奖！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">特别加分项：在昇腾（Ascend）平台成功复现模型，可获高达150分的额外加分！</span></span></strong></p>\n  <ol style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"2\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">创意赛道 (Creativity Track)：全民创作者的脑洞秀</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">参赛方式：不限模型（Sora、可灵、Pika、Runway、Vidu、Pixverse等皆可）、不限主题、不限时长！你只需将AI生成的视频作品发送至官方邮箱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">评审方式：作品将在官方社媒平台（抖音、X/Twitter等）进行公开展播，最终排名由人气决定（观看量、点赞、分享、评论加权计算）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">丰厚奖励：最高可赢取 1万 人民币奖金，另设多个优胜奖项。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">组织者认为，一个真正成熟的视频生成模型，必须能够创造出不仅在视觉上引人入胜，更在逻辑上无懈可击的连贯世界。CVM挑战赛的举办，正是希望为这一目标的实现铺设一条清晰的技术路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当前的视频生成领域也迫切需要一个「北极星」任务来定义标准、凝聚共识、推动发展。CVM挑战赛应运而生，它的目标就是：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为视频生成设立标准化：解决目前各类模型效果难以横向比较的困境。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">攻克核心技术瓶颈：将「一致性」这一模糊概念，量化为可评测的具体指标。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">构建开放协同社区：汇聚全球顶尖智慧，共同推动可信、可靠的AIGC视频技术走向成熟。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说各类文生视频模型的出现，开启了AIGC的「大航海时代」，那么CVM挑战赛，或许就是为这艘巨轮绘制第一张精准航图的开始。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论您是深耕算法的研究者，还是充满奇思妙想的创作者，我们都诚挚地邀请您参与进来，共同定义AI视频生成的未来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">关键时间点：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">报名截止日期：2025年12月25日</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">主赛道初赛：2025年12月25日</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">决赛：2026年1月12日</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大赛详情页：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">[<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/aaai26-cvm]\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/aaai26-cvm]</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">(<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/aaai26-cvm)\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/aaai26-cvm)</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "首个以“一致性”为核心的全球 AI 视频生成挑战赛 CVM（Consistency in Video Generation Models）即将开启，旨在解决 AI 视频生成面临的挑战，并为行业设定标准化评测基准，吸引技术与创意人才参与。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "首个以“一致性”为核心的全球 AI 视频生成挑战赛 CVM（Consistency in Video Generation Models）即将开启，旨在解决 AI 视频生成面临的挑战，并为行业设定标准化评测基准，吸引技术与创意人才参与。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了即将于 AAAI 2026 研讨会期间举行的“从片段到原生：视频生成模型中的一致性（CVM）”全球挑战赛。该赛事由袁粒、颜水成等多位知名学者共同发起，旨在解决 AI 视频生成技术在逻辑、时空、角色风格等方面面临的“一致性”核心挑战，从而提升视频生成质量和应用范围。挑战赛设有侧重模型技术创新的“主赛道”和面向全民创作者的“创意赛道”。大赛强调通过建立标准化评测平台，汇聚全球顶尖学术与产业力量，共同推动 AI 视频生成技术发展，并致力于为该领域设立“北极星”任务和行业标准，以期绘制出 AI 视频生成“大航海时代”的第一张精准航图。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 视频生成领域的核心挑战在于“一致性”问题。",
      "explanation": "当前 AI 视频生成常出现逻辑谬误、时空错乱和角色风格突变，严重影响内容连贯性和可信度，是制约其高质量发展和广泛应用的关键瓶颈，也是 CVM 挑战赛的设立背景。"
    },
    {
      "point": "CVM 挑战赛旨在通过标准化评测平台，解决一致性难题并设立行业基准，成为该领域的“北极星”任务。",
      "explanation": "大赛将复杂的“一致性”概念量化为可评测指标，包括世界知识一致性、镜头一致性和元素 ID 一致性，为 AI 视频生成技术提供明确的发展方向、评估标准和技术路径。"
    },
    {
      "point": "大赛设主赛道和创意赛道，以多元化方式鼓励技术创新和内容创作。",
      "explanation": "主赛道面向技术专家，要求提交模型解决一致性问题，推动技术边界；创意赛道面向所有创作者，不限模型和主题，通过作品评选推广 AI 视频应用和创新。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
